peopleAlsoAsk.question: Do Elvis stamps have any value?
peopleAlsoAsk.snippet:
Dealers sell them to be used as cheap postage. Almost no modern US stamp, unless it contains a genuine error, is worth as much as it cost when it was issued. Factor in inflation and a 29 cent Elvis is worth is worth 3–4 cents in today's money.
Aug 4, 2021
